      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/long-sleeve-swimsuit-the-sulawesi-in-snow-ocean-soul-swimwear-4.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 300,
        "mobile_image_height": 300,
        "title": "Sun Protection Meets Style: UPF 50+ Built In",
        "text": "<p>Our entire collection features UPF 50+ sun protection, helping shield your skin from harmful UV rays. Especially in lighter colours like white, sun protection matters - and our eco-performance fabric does the job naturally, without harsh chemical finishes.</p><p>Pair that with a high neckline or full sleeve for all-day coverage you can rely on.</p>",
