        "desktop_image_height": 300,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable & Ethically Made",
        "text": "<p>Ocean Soul Swimwear is founded on a commitment to the ocean - and that starts with how we make your swimwear. Every white one piece is:</p><p>Econyl®: regenerated nylon from ocean waste<br/></p><p>Lasts twice as long as standard swimwear<br/></p><p>Our sustainable swimwear looks good, feels good, and does good.</p>",
