    "image_with_text_EmjixT": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/khat.mandu_by_fabianmunozhumeres-9.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "A White One Piece That Actually Works for Your Life",
        "text": "<p>If you’ve ever struggled to find a white swimsuit that flatters, stays up, doesn’t go see-through, and actually performs in the water, your search ends here.</p><p>Ocean Soul’s collection of white one piece swimwear is sculpting, ethical, secure - and absolutely stunning. It’s made for the active woman who wants more: more quality, more confidence, and more connection to what she wears.</p><p>Explore the <a href=\"/collections/white-one-piece-swimsuits\" title=\"White One Piece Swimsuits\">collection</a> and find your forever white swimsuit.</p>",
